<div class="modal hide main-modal wizard_modal" id="wizard5" style="background:whitesmoke;position: absolute;top: 600px;left: 800px;overflow:visible;width: 400px;">
  <div class="blue_arrow_dl" style="left:-170px;"></div>
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</button>
    <h3>Was treiben deine Freunde?</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="modal-body" style="background:white;">
    <p>Hier siehst du, wann deine Freunde planen zu arbeiten und kannst dich ihnen anschließen!<br>
      </p>
  </div>

  <div class="modal-footer">
       <button class="continue_button btn btn-primary" data-activate_modal="#wizardx" data-activate_element="#explainx">Weiter</button>

       <button class="continue_button btn" data-activate_modal="#wizard4" data-activate_element="#explain4">Zurück</button>
       <span style="color:#ccc;">5 / 5</span>

  </div><!-- modal-footer -->
</div>
